title: UX Design Workshop
summary: In this workshop we will be going over the best UX practices and talking about new trends and etc…
description: In this workshop we will be going over UX fundamentals. We will go over user flows, users task and etc. We will also be going over the best UX practices and new trends in UX. We will share ideas with each other and we will also be looking at companies with great UX and we will be talking about what makes them so them.
